dct_description_sm: This line data layer represents roads for Door County, Wisconsin in 2006. The dataset was originally published by the Door County Planning and Zoning Department in 2006.[Roads4 is Door County's roads theme for the County. The theme is a work in progress by the Door County Planning Department as the Rural Addressing Program for the County is implemented. The City of Sturgeon Bay and the four Villages in the County will most likely be the last to be updated, as the Door County Planning Department currently administers the Addressing records for the rural portions of the County only. It is the plan of the County to update the City and four Villages, after the Towns have been inventoried and are in a maintenance mode.]
